00:14:53,305 --> 00:14:54,104
Miguel?

281
00:14:54,106 --> 00:14:54,882
Nothing!

282
00:14:56,278 --> 00:14:57,724
Mamá, Papá. I...

283
00:14:57,730 --> 00:15:02,464
Miguel, your Abuelita had the most wonderful idea.

284
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,903
We've all decided.

285
00:15:03,905 --> 00:15:06,775
It's time you joined us in the workshop!

286
00:15:06,815 --> 00:15:07,463
