287
00:15:07,465 --> 00:15:09,095
No more shining shoes.

288
00:15:09,301 --> 00:15:12,064
You'll be making them every day after school.

289
00:15:12,791 --> 00:15:15,003
Our Migueli-ti-ti-ti-to,

290
00:15:15,005 --> 00:15:17,696
