291
00:15:17,821 --> 00:15:20,149
And on Día de los Muertos!

292
00:15:20,151 --> 00:15:22,879
Your ancestors will be so proud.

293
00:15:23,069 --> 00:15:26,507
You'll craft huaraches just like your Tía Victoria.

294
00:15:26,509 --> 00:15:29,183
And wingtips like your Papá Julio.

295
00:15:29,185 --> 00:15:31,810
