314
00:16:38,724 --> 00:16:40,133
Ernesto de la Cruz?

315
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,329
Papá!

316
00:16:41,474 --> 00:16:42,721
Papá!

317
00:16:54,367 --> 00:16:56,450
Papá! Papá! It's him!

318
00:16:56,568 --> 00:16:58,409
I know who my great-great-grandfather was.

319
00:16:58,411 --> 00:17:00,262
Miguel, get down from there.

320
00:17:00,356 --> 00:17:03,062
Mamá Coco's father was Ernesto de la Cruz!

321
00:17:03,064 --> 00:17:04,580
What are you talking about?

322
00:17:04,582 --> 00:17:06,435
I'm gonna be a musician!

323
