353
00:18:19,181 --> 00:18:20,774
Miguel! Miguel!

354
00:18:39,741 --> 00:18:42,385
I want to play in the plaza, like de la Cruz.

355
00:18:42,387 --> 00:18:43,618
Can I still sign up?

356
00:18:43,758 --> 00:18:44,805
You got an instrument?

357
00:18:44,832 --> 00:18:45,649
No.

358
00:18:45,651 --> 00:18:47,587
