361
00:18:51,331 --> 00:18:52,521
I'll put you on the list.

362
00:18:54,967 --> 00:18:57,511
Excuse me. Can I borrow your guitar?

363
00:18:57,513 --> 00:18:58,524
Sorry, muchacho.

364
00:18:58,762 --> 00:19:00,880
You guys have a spare guitar? No.

365
00:19:01,349 --> 00:19:03,544
I need a guitar just for a little bit.

366
00:19:03,546 --> 00:19:05,109
Get out of here, kid.

367
00:19:18,032 --> 00:19:19,551
Great-great-grandfather,

368
00:19:20,895 --> 00:19:22,422
