369
00:19:22,422 --> 00:19:52,422
Subtitle www.movieddl.me

370
00:20:00,533 --> 00:20:02,257
No, no, no, no. Dante, stop!

371
00:20:02,378 --> 00:20:03,264
Cállate! Shut!

372
00:20:25,808 --> 00:20:26,933
I'm sorry.

373
00:21:03,512 --> 00:21:04,987
Senor de la Cruz,

374
00:21:05,967 --> 00:21:07,342
