381
00:21:22,865 --> 00:21:25,192
You would have told me to follow my heart.

382
00:21:25,447 --> 00:21:27,090
To seize my moment!

383
00:21:28,329 --> 00:21:30,785
So, if it's alright with you,

384
00:21:31,217 --> 00:21:32,889
I'm gonna play in the plaza.

385
00:21:32,891 --> 00:21:33,970
Just like you did!

386
00:21:42,468 --> 00:21:43,991
The guitar! It's gone!

387
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:46,815
