00:26:07,827 --> 00:26:09,322
Some churros. From my family.

463
00:26:09,324 --> 00:26:11,167
How wonderful. Next.

464
00:26:11,233 --> 00:26:13,351
If you are experiencing travel issues,

465
00:26:13,353 --> 00:26:15,697
