467
00:26:17,324 --> 00:26:18,821
Next family, please.

468
00:26:23,140 --> 00:26:25,448
Your photos are on your son's ofrenda.

469
00:26:25,450 --> 00:26:26,502
Have a great visit.

470
00:26:26,588 --> 00:26:27,456
Gracias.

471
00:26:27,544 --> 00:26:29,983
And remember to return before sunrise.

472
00:26:29,985 --> 00:26:30,859
Enjoy your visit.

473
00:26:30,861 --> 00:26:31,683
Next.

474
00:26:33,334 --> 00:26:35,448
Your photo's on your dentist's ofrenda.

475
00:26:35,450 --> 00:26:36,745
Enjoy your visit.

476
00:26:36,762 --> 00:26:38,355
Gracias. Next?

477
00:26:40,849 --> 00:26:43,102
Yes! It is I. Frida Kahlo.

478
00:26:43,133 --> 00:26:44,587
Shall we skip the scanner?

479
00:26:44,684 --> 00:26:48,302
I'm on so many ofrendas it'll just overwhelm your blinky thingy.

480
00:26:50,109 --> 00:26:51,096
Well shoot,

481
00:26:51,356 --> 00:26:53,205
looks like no one put up your photo,

482
00:26:53,437 --> 00:26:54,519
Frida.

