487
00:27:00,580 --> 00:27:03,206
No photo on an ofrenda, no crossing the bridge.

488
00:27:03,208 --> 00:27:05,638
You know what, I'm just gonna zip right over.

489
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:07,043
You won't even know I'm gone.

490
00:27:08,418 --> 00:27:09,340
Hey!

491
00:27:15,676 --> 00:27:16,701
Almost...

492
00:27:16,703 --> 00:27:17,390
there.

