00:27:17,462 --> 00:27:19,462
Just a little further.

494
00:27:24,351 --> 00:27:25,523
Upsy-daisy...

495
00:27:25,572 --> 00:27:27,855
Fine. Ok. Fine, who cares?

496
00:27:27,882 --> 00:27:29,549
Dumb flower bridge!

497
00:27:30,668 --> 00:27:33,721
I don't know what I'd do if no one put up my photo.

498
00:27:33,735 --> 00:27:34,417
Next?

499
00:27:34,419 --> 00:27:36,050
Come, mijo. It's our turn.

500
00:27:36,071 --> 00:27:37,703
Welcome back, amigos.

501
00:27:37,705 --> 00:27:39,018
Anything to declare?

502
00:27:39,020 --> 00:27:41,543
As a matter of fact, yes.

503
00:27:42,789 --> 00:27:43,553
Hola.

504
00:27:51,044 --> 00:27:55,720
Paging Marta Gonzales-Ramos. Please report to Level Seven.

505
