510
00:28:26,580 --> 00:28:29,540
I'm sorry señora, it says here no one put up your photo.

511
00:28:29,614 --> 00:28:33,960
My family always, always puts my photo on the ofrenda.

512
00:28:33,962 --> 00:28:36,932
That devil box tells you nothing but lies!

513
00:28:37,090 --> 00:28:38,468
Mamá Imelda?

514
00:28:39,618 --> 00:28:41,642
Oh, mi familia!

515
00:28:41,672 --> 00:28:43,403
