00:28:52,000 --> 00:28:53,843
What? We ran into...

520
00:28:58,820 --> 00:28:59,768
Miguel?

521
00:28:59,770 --> 00:29:01,370
Mamá Imelda.

522
00:29:01,984 --> 00:29:04,157
What is going on?

523
00:29:04,190 --> 00:29:06,223
You the Rivera family?

524
00:29:08,537 --> 00:29:09,765
Well, you're cursed.

525
00:29:10,230 --> 00:29:10,731
What?

526
00:29:10,749 --> 00:29:13,335
Día de los Muertos is the night to give to the dead.

527
00:29:13,337 --> 00:29:14,751
You stole from the dead!

528
00:29:14,753 --> 00:29:17,343
But I wasn't stealing the guitar. Guitar?

529
00:29:17,345 --> 00:29:18,848
It was my great-great-grandfather's.

530
00:29:18,850 --> 00:29:20,438
