♪ Llorona de azul celeste ♪

1497
01:23:08,358 --> 01:23:12,176
♪ Ay de mí Llorona, Llorona ♪

1498
01:23:12,178 --> 01:23:14,899
♪ Llorona de azul celeste ♪

1499
01:23:15,491 --> 01:23:19,337
♪ Y aunque la vida me cueste, Llorona ♪

1500
01:23:19,495 --> 01:23:22,465
♪ No dejaré de quererte ♪

1501
01:23:22,882 --> 01:23:26,557
Let go of me! ♪ Y aunque la vida me cueste, Llorona ♪

1502
01:23:26,877 --> 01:23:30,252
♪ No dejaré de quererte ♪

1503
01:23:30,277 --> 01:23:33,920
♪ No dejaré de quererte ♪

1504
01:23:34,088 --> 01:23:38,486
♪ No dejaré de quererte ♪

1505
01:23:38,764 --> 01:23:41,267
♪ Ay, ay, ay ♪

1506
01:23:50,252 --> 01:23:52,220
I forgot what that felt like.

1507
01:23:52,569 --> 01:23:53,222
You...

1508
01:23:53,914 --> 01:23:55,017
still got it.

1509
01:24:01,078 --> 01:24:03,921
Miguel, I give you my blessing.

1510
01:24:05,457 --> 01:24:06,808
To go home,

1511
01:24:07,389 --> 01:24:11,020
to put up our photos and to never...

1512
01:24:11,022 --> 01:24:13,167
Never play music again.

1513
01:24:14,508 --> 01:24:15,870
To never...

1514
01:24:16,059 --> 01:24:19,231
forget how much your family loves you.

1515
01:24:22,140 --> 01:24:23,437
You're going home.

1516
01:24:26,937 --> 01:24:28,879
You're not going anywhere.

1517
01:24:30,566 --> 01:24:31,596
Imelda!

1518
01:24:31,875 --> 01:24:33,217
Stay back! Stay back!

1519
01:24:33,729 --> 01:24:35,490
All of you, stay back.

1520
01:24:35,861 --> 01:24:37,396
Not one more step.

1521
01:24:39,199 --> 01:24:40,365
Dante!

1522
01:24:42,294 --> 01:24:43,567
Ernesto, stop!

1523
01:24:45,028 --> 01:24:46,263
Leave the boy alone.

1524
01:24:46,331 --> 01:24:48,218
I've worked too hard, Héctor.

1525
01:24:48,220 --> 01:24:50,655
Too hard to let him destroy everything.

1526
01:24:50,657 --> 01:24:52,598
He's a living child, Ernesto.

1527
01:24:52,600 --> 01:24:53,725
He's a threat!

1528
01:24:54,474 --> 01:24:57,941
You think I'd let him go back to the Land of the Living with your photo?

1529
01:24:58,015 --> 01:25:00,306
To keep your memory alive?

1530
01:25:00,308 --> 01:25:01,065
No.

1531
01:25:01,067 --> 01:25:03,781
You're a coward! I am Ernesto de la Cruz.

1532
01:25:03,804 --> 01:25:05,807
The greatest musician of all time!

1533
01:25:05,872 --> 01:25:07,715
Héctor's the real musician.

1534
01:25:07,769 --> 01:25:10,599
You're just the guy who murdered him and stole his songs!

1535
01:25:10,601 --> 01:25:11,277
Murdered?

1536
01:25:11,796 --> 01:25:15,616
I am the one who's willing to do what it takes to seize my moment.

1537
01:25:16,403 --> 01:25:17,754
Whatever it takes.

1538
01:25:20,555 --> 01:25:21,232
No!

1539
01:25:23,285 --> 01:25:24,664
Miguel! Miguel!

1540
01:25:25,655 --> 01:25:27,253
Apologies, old friend.

1541
01:25:27,255 --> 01:25:28,716
But the show must go on.

1542
01:26:11,917 --> 01:26:13,814
Please, please, mi familia.

1543
01:26:13,841 --> 01:26:15,656
Murderer! Get off the stage!

1544
01:26:15,754 --> 01:26:17,835
Orchestra. A-one, a-two, a-one...

1545
01:26:17,934 --> 01:26:19,211
A-one...

1546
01:26:20,738 --> 01:26:23,091
♪ Remember me ♪

1547
01:26:23,093 --> 01:26:24,814
♪ Though I have to s... ♪ Hey!

1548
01:26:26,681 --> 01:26:27,728
Look!

1549
01:26:48,370 --> 01:26:49,322
Nice kitty.

1550
01:26:53,458 --> 01:26:54,841
Put me down!

1551
01:26:54,843 --> 01:26:57,003
No, please! I beg of you! Stop!

1552
01:26:57,123 --> 01:26:58,557
Stop! No!

1553
01:27:06,930 --> 01:27:08,432
No! No!

1554
01:27:20,444 --> 01:27:21,591
What did I miss?

1555
01:27:21,899 --> 01:27:23,367
Good boy, Dante!

1556
01:27:23,468 --> 01:27:24,261
Miguel!

1557
01:27:26,374 --> 01:27:27,458
Héctor!

1558
01:27:28,568 --> 01:27:30,548
The photo... I lost it!

1559
01:27:30,746 --> 01:27:31,518
It's ok, mijo.

1560
01:27:32,186 --> 01:27:33,091
It's o...

1561
01:27:33,693 --> 01:27:34,656
Héctor!

1562
01:27:35,229 --> 01:27:36,339
Héctor?

1563
01:27:37,506 --> 01:27:38,382
Coco.

1564
01:27:38,420 --> 01:27:40,899
No! We can still find the photo.

1565
01:27:40,922 --> 01:27:42,649
Miguel, it's almost sunrise.

1566
01:27:43,842 --> 01:27:45,546
No, no. I can't leave you.

1567
01:27:45,627 --> 01:27:47,716
I promised I'd put your photo up.

1568
01:27:48,001 --> 01:27:50,100
I promised you'd see Coco.

1569
01:27:50,605 --> 01:27:52,239
We're both out of time, mijo.

1570
01:27:53,685 --> 01:27:55,383
Oh no! No!

1571
01:27:55,464 --> 01:27:56,940
She can't forget you!

1572
01:27:57,210 --> 01:27:58,968
I just wanted her to know...

1573
01:27:59,724 --> 01:28:01,337
that I loved her.

1574
01:28:01,943 --> 01:28:03,146
Héctor!

1575
01:28:03,148 --> 01:28:05,495
You have our blessing, Miguel.

1576
01:28:05,947 --> 01:28:07,356
No conditions.

1577
01:28:08,366 --> 01:28:11,085
No! Papá Héctor, please!

1578
01:28:15,332 --> 01:28:16,379
No!

1579
01:28:17,959 --> 01:28:19,135
Go home.

1580
01:28:19,137 --> 01:28:21,806
I promise I won't let Coco forget you!

1581
01:28:49,533 --> 01:28:50,528
There he is!

1582
01:28:51,897 --> 01:28:53,438
Miguel! Stop!

1583
01:28:58,750 --> 01:28:59,935
Where have you been?

1584
01:29:00,055 --> 01:29:01,912
I need to see Mamá Coco, please.

1585
01:29:02,283 --> 01:29:04,574
What are you doing with that... Give it to me!

1586
01:29:05,090 --> 01:29:06,573
Miguel, stop!

1587
01:29:06,575 --> 01:29:08,557
Miguel! Miguel!

1588
01:29:09,208 --> 01:29:10,216
Miguel!

1589
01:29:10,762 --> 01:29:11,725
Mamá Coco?

1590
01:29:11,863 --> 01:29:13,278
Can you hear me?

1591
01:29:13,280 --> 01:29:14,564
It's Miguel.

1592
01:29:15,225 --> 01:29:16,985
I saw your Papá.

1593
01:29:16,987 --> 01:29:18,966
Remember? Papá?

1594
01:29:20,063 --> 01:29:21,127
Please!

1595
01:29:21,755 --> 01:29:22,979
If you forget him,

1596
01:29:22,981 --> 01:29:25,743
he'll be gone. Forever.

1597
01:29:26,078 --> 01:29:27,205
Miguel, open this door!

1598
01:29:27,612 --> 01:29:28,603
Here.

1599
01:29:28,605 --> 01:29:30,373
This was his guitar, right?

1600
01:29:30,375 --> 01:29:32,205
He used to play it to you?

1601
01:29:34,747 --> 01:29:36,589
See? There he is!

1602
01:29:38,066 --> 01:29:40,175
Papá! Remember?

1603
01:29:40,177 --> 01:29:41,143
Papá?

1604
01:29:44,462 --> 01:29:45,457
Miguel!

1605
01:29:45,459 --> 01:29:47,119
Mamá Coco, please!

1606
01:29:47,121 --> 01:29:48,310
Don't forget him.

1607
01:29:55,056 --> 01:29:57,065
What are you doing to that poor woman?

1608
01:29:57,067 --> 01:29:57,856
It's ok, Mamita. It's ok.

1609
01:29:57,976 --> 01:29:59,478
What's gotten into you?

1610
01:30:06,318 --> 01:30:07,762
I thought I'd lost you, Miguel.

